<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Ak Automations API — WhatsApp Cloud API Solution</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/img/favicon.png">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #0a0a0f;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    .bg-glow {
      position: fixed;
      top: -40vh; left: -20vh;
      width: 80vh; height: 80vh;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(37,211,102,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .bg-glow-2 {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: -30vh; right: -20vh;
      width: 70vh; height: 70vh;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,122,255,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 24px 0;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #25D366;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .logo span { color: #fff; }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #25D366; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      border: none;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: #25D366;
      color: #000;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(37,211,102,0.35);
    }
    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
      border-color: #25D366;
      color: #25D366;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 100px 0 80px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      background: rgba(37,211,102,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(37,211,102,0.2);
      color: #25D366;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 56px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -1.5px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }
    .hero h1 em {
      font-style: normal;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #25D366, #1ea854);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .features {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .features h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .features > .container > p {
      text-align: center;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px 28px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(37,211,102,0.2);
      background: rgba(37,211,102,0.03);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .feature-card p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .features-detailed {
      padding: 60px 0 100px;
    }
    .feature-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 60px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }
    .feature-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .feature-row:nth-child(even) { flex-direction: row-reverse; }
    .feature-text { flex: 1; }
    .feature-text h3 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .feature-text p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-right: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .tag-green { background: rgba(37,211,102,0.12); color: #25D366; }
    .tag-blue { background: rgba(0,122,255,0.12); color: #5ac8fa; }
    .tag-purple { background: rgba(175,82,222,0.12); color: #af52de; }
    .tag-orange { background: rgba(255,159,10,0.12); color: #ff9f0a; }
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 0 100px;
    }
    .cta h2 {
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .cta p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      font-size: 13px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 36px; }
      .hero { padding: 60px 0 40px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .feature-row, .feature-row:nth-child(even) { flex-direction: column; gap: 30px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-glow"></div>
  <div class="bg-glow-2"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <nav>
      <div class="logo">Whats<span>API</span></div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#details">Details</a>
        <a href="/dashboard/login" class="btn btn-outline">Login</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-badge">&#9889; Production Ready</div>
      <h1>WhatsApp API <em>Done Right</em></h1>
      <p>Send messages, manage groups, track analytics &mdash; all from one powerful dashboard. Built on Baileys, ready for scale.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/dashboard/login" class="btn btn-primary">Try Dashboard &#8594;</a>
        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore Features</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Everything You Need</h2>
      <p>Full control over your WhatsApp integration</p>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon" style="background:rgba(37,211,102,0.1);color:#25D366;">&#9993;</div>
          <h3>Send Messages</h3>
          <p>Text, images, video, audio, documents &mdash; with captions, mentions, and replies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon" style="background:rgba(0,122,255,0.1);color:#5ac8fa;">&#128101;</div>
          <h3>Group Management</h3>
          <p>Create, edit, invite, promote, demote &mdash; full group CRUD from the API.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon" style="background:rgba(175,82,222,0.1);color:#af52de;">&#128200;</div>
          <h3>Analytics Dashboard</h3>
          <p>Sent/failed counts, queue depth, message history with delete &amp; error tooltips.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon" style="background:rgba(255,159,10,0.1);color:#ff9f0a;">&#9881;</div>
          <h3>Webhook Integration</h3>
          <p>Real-time incoming message forwarding to your own webhook endpoint.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon" style="background:rgba(255,69,58,0.1);color:#ff453a;">&#128196;</div>
          <h3>Google Sheets Ready</h3>
          <p>Built-in Google Apps Script client &mdash; send messages directly from Sheets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon" style="background:rgba(48,209,88,0.1);color:#30d158;">&#9889;</div>
          <h3>Queue &amp; Delay</h3>
          <p>Bull-powered message queue with delay, retries, and in-memory fallback.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features-detailed" id="details">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-row">
        <div class="feature-text">
          <h3>Multi-Instance Architecture</h3>
          <p>Run multiple WhatsApp instances side by side. Each instance gets its own connection, queue, and settings &mdash; fully isolated and independently manageable.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:20px;">
            <span class="tag tag-green">Isolated</span>
            <span class="tag tag-blue">Scalable</span>
            <span class="tag tag-purple">Independent</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-row">
        <div class="feature-text">
          <h3>Flexible Message Delivery</h3>
          <p>Send via URL, file upload, or base64. Support for image, video, audio, document with automatic MIME validation. Queue with optional delay and typing/recording presence.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:20px;">
            <span class="tag tag-green">URL</span>
            <span class="tag tag-blue">File Upload</span>
            <span class="tag tag-orange">Base64</span>
            <span class="tag tag-purple">Delay</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-row">
        <div class="feature-text">
          <h3>Production Security</h3>
          <p>Helmet CSP headers, rate limiting, Bearer token auth, admin token lock, cookie-based dashboard sessions &mdash; built secure by default.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:20px;">
            <span class="tag tag-green">CSP</span>
            <span class="tag tag-blue">Rate Limit</span>
            <span class="tag tag-purple">Auth</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-row">
        <div class="feature-text">
          <h3>Google Apps Script Integration</h3>
          <p>Pre-built <code>WhatsAppAPI.gs</code> client. Call all API functions from Google Sheets with simple formulas like <code>=SEND_TEXT()</code>, <code>=IS_ON_WA()</code>, and <code>=GROUP_SEND()</code>.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:20px;">
            <span class="tag tag-green">SEND_TEXT</span>
            <span class="tag tag-blue">IS_ON_WA</span>
            <span class="tag tag-orange">GROUP_SEND</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p>Login to your dashboard and start sending in minutes.</p>
      <a href="/dashboard/login" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size:18px;padding:16px 48px;">Try Dashboard &#8594;</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      Ak Automations API &mdash; WhatsApp API Management Dashboard
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
